201967,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T23:29:11.000Z","msg":"講笑。<br />\n<br />\nPart A 最頭 10 分淨係用一分鐘，係初中 level，非常簡單。<br />\nPart B 最尾 10 分，就算你 5** 級都要用三十分鐘，時間同分數唔成正比。<br />\n<br />\n所以要 secure level 3，可以先唔理 Part B，淨係做多啲 Part A。<br />\n<br />\n我建議由淺入深，先做好初中嘢，確保 Part A1 有30+/35。然後做 CE past paper，因為比較淺，直至 Part A2 有25/35，已經穩 level 3。頭幾條 Part B，都會比較淺，例如 probit, normal distribution，年年都係咁出，易執分。"},{"pid":"611459bb7edd2cfece23d95020eed08868e276f8","tid":1034324,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T23:49:04.000Z","msg":"由hkcc 入 u 仲好"},{"pid":"bca97b753f4dd956b7495cd4b075db8cee8c9f8a","tid":1034324,"uid":838,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:32:41.000Z","msg":"要將分數控制喺50%至66%左右先攞到3<br />\n其實都唔容易"},{"pid":"aa281619f49d39776bda2868cb041a1fde8530d4","tid":1034324,"uid":228037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"611459bb7edd2cfece23d95020eed08868e276f8","tid":1034324,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T23:49:04.000Z","msg":"由hkcc 入 u 仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"班精英輕鬆入到hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712533ab505c9000b3f83e2770acdfcef1353c75","tid":1034324,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa281619f49d39776bda2868cb041a1fde8530d4","tid":1034324,"uid":228037,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"611459bb7edd2cfece23d95020eed08868e276f8","tid":1034324,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T23:49:04.000Z","msg":"由hkcc 入 u 仲好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:47:56.000Z","msg":"班精英輕鬆入到hku<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"大部份入到三大都first hon grad"},{"pid":"9c26614cee03a51a118c3964df70d6faa68fa5b5","tid":1034324,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"712